                <div class="card__inner">
                    <div class="card__header">
                        <div><span class="card__title">BIL (Blazor Interface Library)</span><p class="card__subtitle">github.com/mjn110/Bil</p></div>
                        <div class="card__chevron"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6" /></svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card__body">Smart UI components for Blazor Server with customizable rendering approach</div>
                    <div class="card__expandable">
                        <div class="card__expandable-inner">
                            <div class="card__expandable-content">
                                <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--muted-fg);line-height:1.7;">A collection of smart UI components developed over Blazor Server to enhance frontend development efficiency. Introduced a customizable rendering approach allowing developers to use or modify components in real time without writing code.</p>
