                        <div class="card__expandable-inner">
                            <div class="card__expandable-content">
                                <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--muted-fg);line-height:1.7;">Utilized various classifiers and feature engineering over input dataset to predict bank customer subscription patterns.</p>
                                <div class="project-links">
                                    <a href="https://github.com/mjn110/SubscriptionClassifier" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-link project-link--gh"><svg class="icon-sm" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 00-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0020 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0019.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 00-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 005 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 00-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 009 18.13V22" /></svg> View Source</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card__overlay"></div><div class="card__corner"></div>
                <div class="card__inner">
                    <div class="card__header">
                        <div><span class="card__title">Todo (Blazor MAUI)</span><p class="card__subtitle">github.com/mjn110/Todo</p></div>
                        <div class="card__chevron"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6" /></svg></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card__body">Cross-platform task management with Clean Architecture</div>
                    <div class="card__expandable">
                        <div class="card__expandable-inner">
                            <div class="card__expandable-content">
                                <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--muted-fg);line-height:1.7;">A task management system produced over a clean architecture in Blazor MAUI. Used different types of APIs to enable component access across platforms.</p>
                                <div class="project-links">
                                    <a href="https://github.com/mjn110/Todo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-link project-link--gh"><svg class="icon-sm" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 00-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0020 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0019.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 00-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 005 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 00-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 009 18.13V22" /></svg> View Source</a>
